own) / pool_broadcast 4 replies distinct ids payload echoed / pool_shutdown -> true + pool_size==0 + all children dead + idempotent. test_channel.hexa 21/21 PASS unchanged (regression 0). 5x runs no flake; 0 leftover /tmp/hexa_chan_* (shutdown channel_close unlinks FIFOs).", "followups": ["channel.ai.md C3 note refresh (this session updated only channel.hexa header @changelog)", "stdlib/cancel wiring (RT-CANCEL-TOKEN)", "dead-cell auto-restart in jsonl_pool", "wilson plugins/swarm/main.hexa de-STUB (use stdlib/jsonl_pool) + wilson build --bundle cell (core/dispatch_table.hexa regen)"], "source": "wilson session — orchestration substrate (G6); see wilson/docs/sessions/2026-05-13-g6-jsonl-pool.md, wilson/docs/hexa-lang-gap-audit.md#g6"}
